55:21.000 --> 55:23.000
Look at what are the trends.

55:23.000 --> 55:28.000
If we take some paper document,

55:28.000 --> 55:30.000
how is it protected?

55:30.000 --> 55:33.000
In principle, it is protected only by access protection.

55:33.000 --> 55:37.000
The maximum you can do with it is lock it in some safe.

55:37.000 --> 55:40.000
Put an armed guard to the safe.

55:40.000 --> 55:42.000
All this is in some controlled territory.

55:42.000 --> 55:45.000
That is, you protect access to this document.

55:45.000 --> 55:52.000
Any security system is initially considered imperfect and imperfect,

55:52.000 --> 55:54.000
because in any case, all this can be hacked.

55:54.000 --> 55:57.000
As soon as the safe is hacked and the document is obtained,

55:57.000 --> 55:59.000
